<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Puzzle Day</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Courier+Prime:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #f5f0e8;
    --paper: #faf7f2;
    --ink: #1a1208;
    --accent: #c8451a;
    --gold: #b8922a;
    --mid: #6b5c3e;
    --light: #e8e0d0;
    --shadow: rgba(26,18,8,0.15);
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    background-image: 
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 50%, rgba(184,146,42,0.06) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, rgba(200,69,26,0.05) 0%, transparent 50%),
      url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%236b5c3e' fill-opacity='0.03'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* ---- VIEWS ---- */
  .view { display: none; min-height: 100vh; }
  .view.active { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

  /* ---- HOME ---- */
  #home {
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .home-inner {
    max-width: 600px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease both;
  }

  .puzzle-icon {
    font-size: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: block;
    animation: spin-in 1s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275) both;
  }

  @keyframes spin-in {
    from { transform: rotate(-180deg) scale(0); opacity: 0; }
    to { transform: rotate(0) scale(1); opacity: 1; }
  }

  .home-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .home-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--mid);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .home-date {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .divider {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    max-width: 300px;
  }
  .divider::before, .divider::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }
  .divider span { color: var(--gold); font-size: 0.8rem; }

  .btn-start {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bg);
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border: none;
    padding: 1.1rem 3rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    position: relative;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--gold);
  }

  .btn-start:hover {
    transform: translate(-2px, -2px);
    box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 var(--gold);
  }

  .btn-start:active {
    transform: translate(2px, 2px);
    box-shadow: 2px 2px 0 var(--gold);
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* ---- PUZZLE LIST ---- */
  #list {
    padding: 0;
  }

  .page-header {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bg);
    padding: 2rem 3rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .back-btn {
    background: none;
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,240,232,0.3);
    color: var(--bg);
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .back-btn:hover { background: rgba(245,240,232,0.1); }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .progress-summary {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .puzzle-list {
    padding: 3rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .puzzle-card {
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 1px solid var(--light);
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 2px 2px 0 var(--light);
    animation: fadeUp 0.4s ease both;
  }

  .puzzle-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.05s; }
  .puzzle-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .puzzle-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
  .puzzle-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .puzzle-card:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.25s; }
  .puzzle-card:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .puzzle-card:nth-child(7) { animation-delay: 0.35s; }
  .puzzle-card:nth-child(8) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
  .puzzle-card:nth-child(9) { animation-delay: 0.45s; }
  .puzzle-card:nth-child(10) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }

  .puzzle-card:hover {
    transform: translate(-2px, -2px);
    box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--gold);
    border-color: var(--gold);
  }

  .puzzle-card.solved {
    border-left: 4px solid #4a7c59;
  }

  .puzzle-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--light);
    min-width: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .puzzle-card.solved .puzzle-num { color: #4a7c59; }

  .puzzle-info { flex: 1; }

  .puzzle-info h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .puzzle-info p {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--mid);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .puzzle-status {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border: 1px solid;
  }

  .status-unsolved { color: var(--mid); border-color: var(--light); }
  .status-solved { color: #4a7c59; border-color: #4a7c59; background: rgba(74,124,89,0.08); }
  .status-revealed { color: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); background: rgba(200,69,26,0.08); }

  .puzzle-arrow { color: var(--gold); font-size: 1.2rem; }

  /* ---- PUZZLE PAGE ---- */
  #puzzle {
    padding: 0;
  }

  .puzzle-content {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem;
    animation: fadeUp 0.4s ease both;
  }

  .puzzle-number-tag {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .puzzle-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .puzzle-type-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border: 1px solid var(--light);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    color: var(--mid);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .puzzle-body {
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 1px solid var(--light);
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .puzzle-body p { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .puzzle-body p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .narrative-chapter {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem !important;
  }

  .narrative {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--mid);
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem !important;
  }

  .puzzle-image {
    width: 100%;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    border: 1px solid var(--light);
    display: block;
  }

  .external-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent);
    padding-bottom: 1px;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .external-link:hover { opacity: 0.7; }

  /* Answer section */
  .answer-section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .answer-section label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mid);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .answer-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .answer-input {
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 1px solid var(--mid);
    padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .answer-input:focus { border-color: var(--ink); }
  .answer-input:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed; }

  .btn-submit {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bg);
    border: none;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.5rem;
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .btn-submit:hover { opacity: 0.8; }
  .btn-submit:disabled { opacity: 0.4; cursor: not-allowed; }

  .answer-feedback {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    display: none;
  }

  .answer-feedback.correct {
    display: block;
    background: rgba(74,124,89,0.12);
    border-left: 3px solid #4a7c59;
    color: #2d5c3a;
  }

  .answer-feedback.incorrect {
    display: block;
    background: rgba(200,69,26,0.08);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* Hints & Reveal */
  .hints-section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hints-header {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mid);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .hint-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .btn-hint {
    background: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--mid);
    color: var(--mid);
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-hint:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .btn-hint.revealed {
    background: rgba(184,146,42,0.1);
    border-color: var(--gold);
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .hint-text {
    background: rgba(184,146,42,0.06);
    border: 1px dashed var(--gold);
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--mid);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    animation: fadeUp 0.3s ease;
  }

  .hint-text span { color: var(--gold); font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }

  /* Reveal answer */
  .reveal-section { border-top: 1px solid var(--light); padding-top: 2rem; }

  .btn-reveal {
    background: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-reveal:hover { background: rgba(200,69,26,0.08); }

  .reveal-confirm {
    display: none;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    background: rgba(200,69,26,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,69,26,0.3);
    padding: 1rem;
    animation: fadeUp 0.3s ease;
  }

  .reveal-confirm p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--mid);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .reveal-confirm-btns { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; }

  .btn-confirm-yes {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: white;
    border: none;
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-confirm-yes:hover { opacity: 0.8; }

  .btn-confirm-no {
    background: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--mid);
    color: var(--mid);
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-confirm-no:hover { border-color: var(--ink); color: var(--ink); }

  .revealed-answer {
    display: none;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: rgba(200,69,26,0.06);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    animation: fadeUp 0.3s ease;
  }

  .revealed-answer span { font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); display: block; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .revealed-answer strong { font-size: 1.1rem; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; }

  /* Modal */
  .modal-overlay {
    display: none;
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(26,18,8,0.6);
    z-index: 100;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .modal-overlay.open { display: flex; }

  .modal {
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 1px solid var(--light);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 400px;
    width: 100%;
    box-shadow: 8px 8px 0 var(--ink);
    animation: fadeUp 0.3s ease;
  }

  .modal p { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.7; }
  .modal-btns { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .puzzle-list { padding: 1.5rem; }
    .puzzle-content { padding: 1.5rem; }
    .page-header { padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; }
    .answer-row { flex-direction: column; }
    .progress-summary { display: none; }
  }

  /* Puzzle navigation */
  .puzzle-nav-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .puzzle-nav-row.top { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .puzzle-nav-row.bottom { margin-top: 2.5rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--light); padding-top: 2rem; }

  .btn-nav {
    background: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--mid);
    color: var(--mid);
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-nav:hover { border-color: var(--ink); color: var(--ink); }

  .btn-nav.next {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bg);
    border-color: var(--ink);
  }

  .btn-nav.next:hover {
    background: var(--mid);
    border-color: var(--mid);
  }

  .btn-nav.invisible { visibility: hidden; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HOME VIEW -->
<div id="home" class="view active">
  <div class="home-inner">
    <span class="puzzle-icon">🧩</span>
    <h1 class="home-title">Puzzle Day</h1>
    <p class="home-subtitle">A day of riddles, mysteries & mischief</p>
    <p class="home-date">— an unofficial holiday —</p>
    <div class="divider"><span>✦</span></div>
    <button class="btn-start" onclick="showList()">Start Puzzles</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- PUZZLE LIST VIEW -->
<div id="list" class="view">
  <div class="page-header">
    <button class="back-btn" onclick="showHome()">← Home</button>
    <h1>The Puzzles</h1>
    <span class="progress-summary" id="progress-text">0 / 10 solved</span>
  </div>
  <div class="puzzle-list" id="puzzle-list">
    <!-- Generated by JS -->
  </div>
</div>

<!-- PUZZLE VIEW -->
<div id="puzzle" class="view">
  <div class="page-header">
    <button class="back-btn" onclick="showList()">← All Puzzles</button>
    <h1 id="puzzle-nav-title">Puzzle</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="puzzle-content" id="puzzle-content">
    <!-- Generated by JS -->
  </div>
</div>

<!-- REVEAL CONFIRM MODAL -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="reveal-modal">
  <div class="modal">
    <p>Are you sure you want to reveal the answer? This will mark the puzzle as revealed rather than solved.</p>
    <div class="modal-btns">
      <button class="btn-confirm-yes" onclick="confirmReveal()">Yes, reveal it</button>
      <button class="btn-confirm-no" onclick="closeRevealModal()">No, keep trying</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SPOILER WARNING MODAL -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="spoiler-modal">
  <div class="modal">
    <p id="spoiler-modal-text">The next puzzle may contain spoilers for this one. Are you sure you want to continue?</p>
    <div class="modal-btns">
      <button class="btn-confirm-yes" onclick="confirmSpoiler()">Continue anyway</button>
      <button class="btn-confirm-no" onclick="closeSpoilerModal()">Go back</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
const PUZZLES = [
  {
    id: 1,
    title: "The Mini Crossword",
    type: "Online Puzzle",
    description: `<p class="narrative-chapter">Chapter 1</p>
    <p class="narrative">At precisely 7:42am on 9 March, Matthew's radio alarm clicked on with the reassuring seriousness of BBC Radio 4.</p>
    <p class="narrative">"…and in local news, residents of Amersham have reported a number of statistically improbable events overnight…"</p>
    <p class="narrative">Matthew did not register this. It was Monday morning after all.</p>
    <p class="narrative">"…life expectancy in the HP6 postcode appears to have adjusted unexpectedly…"</p>
    <p class="narrative">He pressed snooze.</p>
    <p class="narrative">Four minutes later, he woke properly, silenced the radio, and reached for his bedside notebook labelled PUZZLE DAY. He had waited for this day for months, and was determined to do a puzzle before engaging in ordinary life.</p>
    <p class="narrative">He unfolded the mini crossword.</p>
    <hr style="border:none; border-top: 1px dashed var(--light); margin: 1.5rem 0;">
    <p style="text-align:center; margin: 1.5rem 0;">
      <a class="external-link" href="https://crosshare.org/crosswords/kxrNkJJvLQMpDd5YObD6/puzzle-day" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        → Open the Mini Crossword ↗
      </a>
    </p>
    <p>Once you've completed it, come back here and enter the answer to <strong>5 Down</strong>.</p>`,
    answer: "eased",
    acceptableAnswers: ["eased", "EASED"],
    hints: []
  },
  {
    id: 2,
    title: "The Chess Puzzle",
    type: "Chess",
    description: `<p class="narrative-chapter">Chapter 2</p>
    <p class="narrative">The crossword done, and feeling distinctly eased into consciousness, Matthew rose with purpose. Puzzle Day required standards. He shaved with actuarial precision, knotted his tie in a sensible half-Windsor, and selected his favourite pair of Doctor Who cufflinks — tiny silver Daleks that looked faintly judgemental.</p>
    <p class="narrative">On his walk to the office, he passed the couple he saw every morning: tall man, cheerful woman, an aura of joint ISA contributions. Except today something felt… adjusted.</p>
    <p class="narrative">While the couple normally appeared roughly the same age, the woman looked subtly younger than usual. Not dramatically. Just… statistically tidier.</p>
    <p class="narrative">"New haircut," Matthew muttered confidently, because the alternative was nonsense.</p>
    <p class="narrative">Further down the road, he noticed something else. The queue at the bus stop appeared to be arranged strictly by increasing age. A teenager stood at the very front, earphones in. Behind him, a neat gradient of commuters progressed steadily toward pensioners.</p>
